1
00:00:12,625 --> 00:00:17,000
[explosions]

2
00:00:17,083 --> 00:00:27,041
♪

3
00:00:33,666 --> 00:00:36,666
[DOMINATOR] Enforcement mode:
Destroy Decomposer.

4
00:00:36,750 --> 00:00:38,916
Target will be
completely annihilated.

5
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:41,291
Aim carefully and
eliminate the target.

6
00:00:47,708 --> 00:00:49,416
[rumble]

7
00:00:50,541 --> 00:00:54,208
[AKANE] Ms. Karanomori.
Are you certain?

8
00:00:54,291 --> 00:00:56,500
Yep. The people who
are remotely operating

9
00:00:56,583 --> 00:00:57,916
those Drones are--

10
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:02,041
[beeping from game]

11
00:01:02,125 --> 00:01:03,125
[BOY STUDENT A grunts]

12
00:01:03,208 --> 00:01:04,666
Crap! Where did he go?

13
00:01:04,750 --> 00:01:05,625
Quick, find him!

14
00:01:05,708 --> 00:01:07,083
I got him!

15
00:01:08,750 --> 00:01:10,125
[BOY STUDENT B] On your right!

16
00:01:11,541 --> 00:01:15,541
♪

17
00:01:15,625 --> 00:01:17,708
Wait, civilians are doing this?

18
00:01:21,625 --> 00:01:24,750
Bastard! You're
scrap metal now!

19
00:01:24,833 --> 00:01:26,500
[SUGO] Wait! Don't chase it!

20
00:01:26,583 --> 00:01:28,375
Hasuike!

21
00:01:28,458 --> 00:01:29,500
[BOY STUDENT F] Damn it!

22
00:01:29,583 --> 00:01:31,833
[BOY STUDENT G] Run faster!

23
00:01:31,916 --> 00:01:34,000
[SHION] The Ministry of
National Defense's Drones

24
00:01:34,083 --> 00:01:35,916
getting hijacked
is alarming enough.

25
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:38,083
But add to that a
horde of random citizens

26
00:01:38,166 --> 00:01:41,250
controlling them? Why,
it's simply unimaginable.

27
00:01:43,333 --> 00:01:44,541
[SHION] They probably
aren't even aware

28
00:01:44,625 --> 00:01:45,791
of what they're doing.

29
00:01:45,875 --> 00:01:47,708
It's using a protection
program designed

30
00:01:47,791 --> 00:01:50,500
for border security
Drone operators.

31
00:01:51,958 --> 00:01:53,416
Protection program?

32
00:01:53,500 --> 00:01:56,208
[SHION] It converts video into
virtual Holo representations

33
00:01:56,291 --> 00:01:57,875
to keep the
operator's Psycho-Pass

34
00:01:57,958 --> 00:01:59,333
from getting clouded.

35
00:01:59,416 --> 00:02:01,166
It's making the
Drone's camera feed

36
00:02:01,250 --> 00:02:03,208
look like a cute video game.

37
00:02:03,291 --> 00:02:06,666
[AKANE] People who kill
without the intent to kill.

38
00:02:06,750 --> 00:02:09,041
What color are those people?

39
00:02:09,125 --> 00:02:11,000
Is that what you were asking...

40
00:02:13,041 --> 00:02:14,416
[AKANE] Kamui?

41
00:03:45,541 --> 00:03:47,583
[SHION] The game's been
posted to multiple sites.

42
00:03:47,666 --> 00:03:50,583
And every time I delete it,
it gets uploaded again.

43
00:03:50,916 --> 00:03:54,083
[music from game]

44
00:03:54,166 --> 00:03:56,041
[SHION]
I'm chasing my tail here.

45
00:03:56,125 --> 00:03:58,083
It's only a matter of
time before all the Drones

46
00:03:58,166 --> 00:04:00,083
at the port have been hijacked.

47
00:04:01,166 --> 00:04:02,583
[AKANE] Is there any way
for you to seize control

48
00:04:02,666 --> 00:04:03,750
and shut them down?

49
00:04:03,833 --> 00:04:06,000
Well, let's see
it's a cloud-based app--

50
00:04:06,083 --> 00:04:08,791
so if I can gain access
to the cloud server.

51
00:04:08,875 --> 00:04:10,458
[SHION] Unfortunately,
they've gone to great lengths

52
00:04:10,541 --> 00:04:14,208
to mask the server's location,
so I'm gonna need some time.

53
00:04:14,291 --> 00:04:15,958
[AKANE] Please work
as fast as you can.

54
00:04:16,041 --> 00:04:17,416
And try to warn the players.

55
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:19,875
We have to stop it
from spreading further.

56
00:04:19,958 --> 00:04:22,625
These can only fire
three Decomposer shots.

57
00:04:22,708 --> 00:04:24,750
That does put
us in quite a bind.

58
00:04:24,833 --> 00:04:27,750
Yeah. I think we should
all get out of here now.

59
00:04:33,750 --> 00:04:34,916
Was that your intent?

60
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:37,875
To lure the PSB
into a hunting game?

61
00:04:40,916 --> 00:04:44,250
I think not. There's
more to it than that.

62
00:04:45,666 --> 00:04:48,166
[AKANE] Kamui's been
experimenting with Dominators.

63
00:04:48,250 --> 00:04:50,875
Figuring out how they work.

64
00:04:50,958 --> 00:04:52,916
He must know by now
that we can disable Drones

65
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:55,583
with Decomposers, and yet...

66
00:04:55,666 --> 00:04:58,250
You think he's playing
a bigger game here?

67
00:05:01,041 --> 00:05:02,583
[gasps]

68
00:05:02,666 --> 00:05:04,208
[AKANE]
Attention, all Enforcers!

69
00:05:04,291 --> 00:05:05,791
Do not go off on your own!

70
00:05:05,875 --> 00:05:08,791
You must remain with
an Inspector at all times!

71
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:11,375
[AKANE] The Drones
are just decoys!

72
00:05:11,458 --> 00:05:14,041
A human with a Dominator
is the real danger!

73
00:05:14,666 --> 00:05:17,791
[rumble]

74
00:05:17,875 --> 00:05:21,666
[HASUIKE panting]

75
00:05:21,750 --> 00:05:23,666
Heh.

76
00:05:23,750 --> 00:05:26,166
[DOMINATOR] Crime Coefficient:
Three hundred twenty-two.

77
00:05:26,250 --> 00:05:28,958
Enforcement mode.
Lethal Eliminator.

78
00:05:29,583 --> 00:05:31,666
Ah! You're kidding me.

79
00:05:34,208 --> 00:05:37,125
[HASUIKE groans]

80
00:05:37,208 --> 00:05:40,500
[yells]

81
00:05:41,875 --> 00:05:47,333
[screaming]

82
00:05:47,416 --> 00:05:50,000
[HASUIKE] Inspector... Shisui?

83
00:05:50,083 --> 00:05:51,791
In the world Kamui's creating,

84
00:05:51,875 --> 00:05:53,916
hunting dogs aren't needed.

85
00:05:54,666 --> 00:05:58,333
[labored breathing]

86
00:05:59,291 --> 00:06:01,291
How are you feeling now?

87
00:06:01,375 --> 00:06:04,250
I feel absolutely fine.
I don't need a scan

88
00:06:04,333 --> 00:06:08,166
to tell me that my
Psycho-Pass is still clear.

89
00:06:08,250 --> 00:06:09,875
[KAMUI] The clarity
you're feeling...

90
00:06:09,958 --> 00:06:12,708
that's the mind
you were born with.

91
00:06:12,791 --> 00:06:16,750
You've finally been
released. Congratulations.

92
00:06:16,833 --> 00:06:20,458
[SHISUI] It's all
thanks to you, Kamui.

93
00:06:20,541 --> 00:06:23,500
[KAMUI] I don't
deserve such gratitude.

94
00:06:23,583 --> 00:06:27,291
Not after that. I did
a terrible thing to you.

95
00:06:27,375 --> 00:06:33,250
It's okay. All my life,
I never liked my eyes.

96
00:06:33,333 --> 00:06:36,583
[DOMINATOR] User authentication,
Inspector Mizue Shisui.

97
00:06:36,666 --> 00:06:38,791
Dominator usage approved.

98
00:06:42,541 --> 00:06:45,750
[KAMUI] For me, your eye
is of critical importance.

99
00:06:48,041 --> 00:06:50,333
[KAMUI] It's perfect.

100
00:06:50,416 --> 00:06:52,416
With its help, this Dominator

101
00:06:52,500 --> 00:06:55,666
will always identify me as you.

102
00:06:55,750 --> 00:06:58,708
I'm glad my eye could
become part of you.

103
00:06:58,791 --> 00:07:00,583
[SHISUI] If I can be
of any more use to you,

104
00:07:00,666 --> 00:07:02,833
please use my body as you wish.

105
00:07:02,916 --> 00:07:06,958
[KAMUI] Thank you. For now, we
should proceed with our plan.

106
00:07:08,333 --> 00:07:10,416
[SAKUYA] So if this isn't
about just killing Enforcers,

107
00:07:10,500 --> 00:07:11,916
what is Kamui's goal?

108
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:14,625
If we take all his
attacks into account,

109
00:07:14,708 --> 00:07:17,166
[AKANE] only
one goal makes sense.

110
00:07:18,250 --> 00:07:21,166
Okay, I understand.

111
00:07:21,250 --> 00:07:23,833
[SAIGA] I know what
your boss is doing.

112
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:28,583
[AKANE] He's
collecting Dominators.

113
00:07:28,666 --> 00:07:36,625
♪

114
00:07:36,708 --> 00:07:39,083
He's been tracking
her Psycho-Pass levels

115
00:07:39,166 --> 00:07:40,791
all this time.

116
00:07:40,875 --> 00:07:43,208
[MIKA] Since he came here.

117
00:07:43,291 --> 00:07:46,291
Every day? Creepy!

118
00:07:46,375 --> 00:07:51,916
[digital beeping]

119
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:55,083
[SHION] Mika! Where the
hell did you run off to?

120
00:07:55,166 --> 00:07:58,125
Why aren't you out in the field
with your senior Inspector?

121
00:07:58,208 --> 00:07:59,583
Huh?

122
00:08:01,125 --> 00:08:02,333
[computer keyboard clicking]

123
00:08:02,416 --> 00:08:03,625
[KUNIZUKA] I don't get it.

124
00:08:03,708 --> 00:08:07,041
Inspector Shisui has
activated two Dominators.

125
00:08:07,125 --> 00:08:09,041
And they're moving
in two directions.

126
00:08:09,125 --> 00:08:11,208
It means somebody's
stolen her identity,

127
00:08:11,291 --> 00:08:13,458
so they can use a
Dominator in her place.

128
00:08:13,541 --> 00:08:15,625
Impossible.

129
00:08:15,708 --> 00:08:19,041
[SHION] So we thought,
but it's the only explanation.

130
00:08:19,125 --> 00:08:21,458
I'll wait for
Shimotsuki to get here,

131
00:08:21,541 --> 00:08:22,625
and then we'll move in.

132
00:08:22,708 --> 00:08:24,583
[AKANE] Negative.

133
00:08:24,666 --> 00:08:26,416
As long as he
has a Dominator,

134
00:08:26,500 --> 00:08:28,625
all Enforcers should stay back!

135
00:08:32,333 --> 00:08:34,125
[groans]

136
00:08:34,208 --> 00:08:36,500
[screaming]

137
00:08:38,708 --> 00:08:39,916
Aikawa!

138
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:42,291
[groans]

139
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:54,000
♪

140
00:09:01,833 --> 00:09:04,500
[DISTRICT THREE
INSPECTOR groans]

141
00:09:07,958 --> 00:09:08,875
[GINOZA] Tsunemori!

142
00:09:08,958 --> 00:09:09,958
[AKANE] Ginoza!

143
00:09:10,041 --> 00:09:11,416
[GINOZA] You okay?

144
00:09:13,041 --> 00:09:14,625
[GINOZA] Both of the
Division Three Inspectors

145
00:09:14,708 --> 00:09:17,166
are out of action. What now?

146
00:09:17,250 --> 00:09:21,416
[AKANE] Karanomori. Lock in
on both Shisui's Dominators.

147
00:09:21,500 --> 00:09:23,916
And send the
location to us.

148
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,958
Do you want
to attack them?

149
00:09:26,041 --> 00:09:27,500
[AKANE] You guys
get out of here.

150
00:09:27,583 --> 00:09:30,000
Your safety's the most
important thing right now.

151
00:09:30,083 --> 00:09:32,958
Akane, please
don't do this!

152
00:09:33,041 --> 00:09:35,791
An Inspector can't be
killed by a Dominator.

153
00:09:35,875 --> 00:09:38,625
I have to! I'll capture Kamui.

154
00:09:41,125 --> 00:09:43,208
[MIKA]
She's gone off the deep end.

155
00:09:43,291 --> 00:09:46,708
Standing down the Enforcers
and chasing Kamui by herself.

156
00:09:46,791 --> 00:09:48,583
Thinking she's
so smart and capable

157
00:09:48,666 --> 00:09:50,958
with her perfect
little Psycho-Pass.

158
00:09:51,041 --> 00:09:52,666
I hope it clouds up.

159
00:09:55,666 --> 00:09:58,875
[MIKA] Wait. I shouldn't
say stuff like that.

160
00:10:00,791 --> 00:10:02,666
[KUNIZUKA]
Her plan is crazy!

161
00:10:02,750 --> 00:10:05,333
Those Dominators are guarded
by a whole army of Drones!

162
00:10:05,416 --> 00:10:06,708
[door opens]

163
00:10:06,791 --> 00:10:08,541
[SAIGA] So, the cloud
server that game's on--

164
00:10:08,625 --> 00:10:11,125
Is it possible it's
been right in front of us?

165
00:10:11,208 --> 00:10:13,375
[gasps] That's right!

166
00:10:14,416 --> 00:10:17,083
[SHION] Why didn't I think
of this potential lead before?

167
00:10:17,166 --> 00:10:18,958
If the Drones are
controlled by a server

168
00:10:19,041 --> 00:10:20,541
in the Ministry
of National Defense,

169
00:10:20,625 --> 00:10:23,208
then that would mean--

170
00:10:23,291 --> 00:10:24,541
Bingo!

171
00:10:24,625 --> 00:10:25,791
[gasps]

172
00:10:25,875 --> 00:10:28,583
Now crack the code and
turn off the display Holo.

173
00:10:28,666 --> 00:10:31,125
We don't want any
Psycho-Pass protection.

174
00:10:31,208 --> 00:10:32,708
Hold on, Professor.

175
00:10:32,791 --> 00:10:34,916
You want the players
to see all the killing?

176
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:37,583
It's the fastest way
to stop this madness.

177
00:10:37,666 --> 00:10:40,333
The Defense Ministry
isn't doing us any favors.

178
00:10:40,416 --> 00:10:42,000
Terminating the
Holo is gonna require

179
00:10:42,083 --> 00:10:44,208
[SHION]
some heavy duty hacking.

180
00:10:44,291 --> 00:10:46,833
[HINAKAWA]
Hey. I think I can do it.

181
00:10:46,916 --> 00:10:49,458
You think, or you know?

182
00:10:49,541 --> 00:10:51,916
I know. I can
help "Big Sis."

183
00:10:53,208 --> 00:10:55,208
Good. Then I'll help him.

184
00:10:55,291 --> 00:11:00,916
♪

185
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,958
[ALL] Huh?
[BOY STUDENT C] Whoa!

186
00:11:03,041 --> 00:11:09,791
♪

187
00:11:09,875 --> 00:11:11,416
[panting]

188
00:11:11,500 --> 00:11:12,958
[SHION] Akane,
go to the end of the path

189
00:11:13,041 --> 00:11:14,291
and turn right at the hangar.

190
00:11:14,375 --> 00:11:17,000
There are fewer
Drones on that side!

191
00:11:17,083 --> 00:11:18,500
[KUNIZUKA] We got
eight playable Holos,

192
00:11:18,583 --> 00:11:20,625
each one comprised
of fifteen layers.

193
00:11:20,708 --> 00:11:23,166
And we have to analyze
all of them quickly!

194
00:11:23,250 --> 00:11:25,500
Yes. I know.

195
00:11:25,583 --> 00:11:31,375
♪

196
00:11:31,458 --> 00:11:32,833
Mmm!

197
00:11:34,958 --> 00:11:36,083
[SUGO panting]

198
00:11:36,166 --> 00:11:37,500
[grunts]

199
00:11:37,583 --> 00:11:42,333
♪

200
00:11:42,416 --> 00:11:44,125
[AKANE] Mr. Sugo!

201
00:11:44,208 --> 00:11:45,583
[SUGO] Get up!

202
00:11:47,958 --> 00:11:49,791
Hey! Why can't
I shoot anymore?

203
00:11:49,875 --> 00:11:52,291
[DOMINATOR] Enforcement mode:
Destroy Decomposer.

204
00:11:52,375 --> 00:11:54,166
Target will be
completely annihilated.

205
00:11:54,250 --> 00:11:56,541
Aim carefully and
elimate the target.

206
00:12:00,208 --> 00:12:01,250
[beeping from game]

207
00:12:01,333 --> 00:12:02,958
[MAN] Oh, come on!
[beeping from game]

208
00:12:03,041 --> 00:12:07,083
[panting]

209
00:12:07,166 --> 00:12:08,416
[SAKUYA] Inspector!

210
00:12:08,500 --> 00:12:10,041
[AKANE] Mr. Togane!

211
00:12:10,125 --> 00:12:12,250
[GINOZA] An Inspector's
job is to babysit.

212
00:12:12,333 --> 00:12:13,666
[AKANE] Ginoza!

213
00:12:13,750 --> 00:12:15,625
[GINOZA] Let us
do what we're good at.

214
00:12:15,708 --> 00:12:17,666
[SAKUYA] Hold on.
What just happened?

215
00:12:17,750 --> 00:12:21,083
A safety mechanism keeps the
drones from shooting each other.

216
00:12:21,166 --> 00:12:22,583
[SUGO] When two or
more of the same type are

217
00:12:22,666 --> 00:12:24,541
within a certain radius...

218
00:12:24,625 --> 00:12:27,750
their guns are designed
to automatically lock up.

219
00:12:27,833 --> 00:12:30,208
You sure know this place well.

220
00:12:30,291 --> 00:12:31,250
[AKANE] So?

221
00:12:31,333 --> 00:12:33,791
Yes. I might have a plan.

222
00:12:33,875 --> 00:12:37,541
[SUGO] There may be a way
for me to disable the Drones.

223
00:12:37,625 --> 00:12:39,583
What do you mean "may"?

224
00:12:39,666 --> 00:12:41,083
And what happens
if you fail?

225
00:12:41,166 --> 00:12:42,875
Well then,
I'll die, that's all.

226
00:12:42,958 --> 00:12:44,875
Wouldn't be much of a loss.

227
00:12:46,583 --> 00:12:50,125
Enforcer Sugo, tell me
your plan, and I'll handle it.

228
00:12:50,208 --> 00:12:51,041
[gasps]

229
00:12:51,125 --> 00:12:52,250
Tsunemori!

230
00:12:52,333 --> 00:12:53,750
[digital beeping]

231
00:12:53,833 --> 00:12:55,666
[MAN] This is Shinjo,
Division Three.

232
00:12:55,750 --> 00:12:58,000
Everyone here's dead. Please!

233
00:12:58,083 --> 00:12:59,416
Help me!

234
00:12:59,500 --> 00:13:01,500
[AKANE] Calm down.
We're on our way to you now.

235
00:13:01,583 --> 00:13:02,416
[distant footsteps]

236
00:13:02,500 --> 00:13:03,916
Huh?
[distant footsteps]

237
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:05,791
[SHINJO panicked gasps]
[distant footsteps]

238
00:13:05,875 --> 00:13:07,833
[DOMINATOR] Crime Coefficient.
Three hundred eleven.

239
00:13:07,916 --> 00:13:10,708
Enforcement mode:
Lethal Eliminator.

240
00:13:10,791 --> 00:13:14,625
[grunts] Crap! Crap! Crap!

241
00:13:14,708 --> 00:13:16,125
[SHINJO] No--!

242
00:13:17,791 --> 00:13:20,583
Enforcer Shinjo, come in!

243
00:13:21,583 --> 00:13:23,916
Enforcer Shinjo!

244
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:26,041
[AKANE] Mister Sugo,
I'm ordering you!

245
00:13:26,125 --> 00:13:27,458
Give me the instructions!

246
00:13:27,541 --> 00:13:28,750
But ma'am, I--

247
00:13:28,833 --> 00:13:31,500
Tsunemori, there's no
need for you to do this.

248
00:13:31,583 --> 00:13:35,000
Hurry! Before there're
any more victims here!

249
00:13:38,791 --> 00:13:40,208
All right, fine.

250
00:13:40,291 --> 00:13:42,416
There's a testing area.
It's up ahead.

251
00:13:42,500 --> 00:13:43,458
[AKANE] Let's go.

252
00:13:43,541 --> 00:13:46,333
Hey, wait! Stay
close and be careful!

253
00:13:47,750 --> 00:13:50,125
[Dominator beeping]

254
00:13:50,208 --> 00:13:52,125
[SAKUYA] Hm.

255
00:13:52,208 --> 00:13:55,916
Even at a time like this,
she's crystal clear.

256
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:59,208
[SAKUYA] Which is precisely
why I want to color her black.

257
00:14:00,250 --> 00:14:07,166
[music and beeping from game]

258
00:14:07,250 --> 00:14:09,500
[SUGO] The Drones are all
following Inspector Tsunemori.

259
00:14:09,583 --> 00:14:11,875
We can use that
to lure them in here.

260
00:14:14,500 --> 00:14:16,041
Well?

261
00:14:18,208 --> 00:14:20,291
[SUGO] Drone firearms.

262
00:14:22,666 --> 00:14:25,166
[SHION] Okay, Akane,
that's good. Keep it up.

263
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:29,291
What the--?

264
00:14:29,375 --> 00:14:32,166
♪

265
00:14:32,250 --> 00:14:35,958
[AKANE'S running footsteps]

266
00:14:36,041 --> 00:14:39,958
♪

267
00:14:40,041 --> 00:14:42,875
[beeping from game]

268
00:14:42,958 --> 00:14:53,000
♪

269
00:14:53,083 --> 00:14:55,166
[panting]

270
00:14:55,250 --> 00:15:05,208
♪

271
00:15:08,333 --> 00:15:11,208
[DOMINATOR] Enforcement mode.
Destroy Decomposer.

272
00:15:11,291 --> 00:15:13,875
Target will be
completely annihilated.

273
00:15:15,750 --> 00:15:17,125
[grunts]

274
00:15:18,500 --> 00:15:19,833
Now!

275
00:15:19,916 --> 00:15:29,875
♪

276
00:15:37,625 --> 00:15:39,000
[AKANE] Uh!

277
00:15:41,333 --> 00:15:42,750
[GINOZA groans]

278
00:15:44,291 --> 00:15:46,041
[commotion]

279
00:15:46,125 --> 00:15:49,166
[beeping tune]

280
00:15:49,250 --> 00:15:50,875
Over where
Inspector Shisui is,

281
00:15:50,958 --> 00:15:53,333
I'm seeing five
Dominators clustered.

282
00:15:53,416 --> 00:15:55,375
I bet Kamui's there, too.

283
00:15:55,458 --> 00:15:56,625
[GINOZA] I think
we've taken care of

284
00:15:56,708 --> 00:15:58,833
just about all the Drones here.

285
00:15:58,916 --> 00:16:00,291
[SHION] They're
heading for the docks.

286
00:16:00,375 --> 00:16:02,333
Could be planning
to escape by sea.

287
00:16:05,666 --> 00:16:08,458
[GINOZA] Whoa, hold on.
What're you gonna do with that?

288
00:16:08,541 --> 00:16:11,583
I don't think our
Dominators will work on Kamui.

289
00:16:12,625 --> 00:16:14,791
Do this and you'll
ruin your Psycho-Pass.

290
00:16:14,875 --> 00:16:16,541
I'll take my chances.

291
00:16:16,625 --> 00:16:17,791
Of course.

292
00:16:17,875 --> 00:16:19,250
[SAKUYA] Hey, look.

293
00:16:21,708 --> 00:16:23,416
[electronic beeping]

294
00:16:23,500 --> 00:16:25,333
[music from game begins]

295
00:16:25,416 --> 00:16:27,583
[MAN] Hey, free continue!

296
00:16:29,583 --> 00:16:31,708
[FEMALE NURSE] Ah...!

297
00:16:31,791 --> 00:16:34,291
They've taken over
our Drone network, too.

298
00:16:36,208 --> 00:16:38,625
[SHION] We're losing
control of the situation.

299
00:16:38,708 --> 00:16:48,666
♪

300
00:16:49,791 --> 00:16:51,541
Hey! Guys!

301
00:16:51,625 --> 00:16:52,750
It's done!

302
00:16:52,833 --> 00:16:54,166
[KUNIZUKA] We're sending
it your way, Shion!

303
00:16:54,250 --> 00:16:56,125
[SHION] You just
saved our asses, Sho!

304
00:16:56,208 --> 00:16:58,708
[SAIGA] Great! Terminate
the game screen Holos as fast

305
00:16:58,791 --> 00:17:01,333
as you can!
Time to lift the curtain.

306
00:17:01,416 --> 00:17:03,583
What? We can't show the
players what they've done

307
00:17:03,666 --> 00:17:05,708
with those Drones in real life!

308
00:17:05,791 --> 00:17:07,708
Do you have any idea
how many Psycho-Passes

309
00:17:07,791 --> 00:17:09,250
[MIKA] that will cloud?!

310
00:17:14,458 --> 00:17:17,000
Dealing with the fallout
from that is your problem.

311
00:17:17,083 --> 00:17:18,458
[MIKA] What?

312
00:17:18,875 --> 00:17:20,916
If we do nothing, they'll
eventually take control

313
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:23,750
of all the Drones we
have. Do you want that?

314
00:17:23,833 --> 00:17:25,625
[MAN groaning]

315
00:17:27,041 --> 00:17:29,791
[MIKA] Our job isn't to make
people's Psycho-Passes worse!

316
00:17:29,875 --> 00:17:31,625
Not all problems, my dear,

317
00:17:31,708 --> 00:17:35,041
can be solved going by the book.

318
00:17:35,125 --> 00:17:36,416
[exhales heavily]

319
00:17:37,583 --> 00:17:40,125
[groaning]

320
00:17:40,208 --> 00:17:41,500
[SUGO grunts]

321
00:17:41,583 --> 00:17:43,541
Damn! I'm all out!

322
00:17:54,416 --> 00:17:56,583
[SUGO] I'm sorry,
Enforcer Ginoza.

323
00:17:56,666 --> 00:17:58,708
[GINOZA]
Just shut up and move!

324
00:18:01,750 --> 00:18:04,125
[SHION] Okay!
Here goes nothing!

325
00:18:07,083 --> 00:18:08,458
[SHION] Heh.

326
00:18:13,666 --> 00:18:15,041
[ALL gasp]

327
00:18:15,125 --> 00:18:25,083
♪

328
00:18:32,250 --> 00:18:34,416
[MAN retches]

329
00:18:34,500 --> 00:18:36,916
[BOY STUDENT E] What the
hell happened to our game?

330
00:18:38,041 --> 00:18:40,083
[CIVILIANS ON SCREEN groaning]

331
00:18:40,166 --> 00:18:43,291
[yowling]

332
00:18:46,250 --> 00:18:49,166
[panting]

333
00:18:49,250 --> 00:18:51,166
[AKANE] The Drones
have stopped moving!

334
00:18:51,250 --> 00:18:52,625
[SHION chuckles]

335
00:18:52,708 --> 00:18:54,125
Wait, look!

336
00:18:54,208 --> 00:18:57,000
[FEMALE ANNOUNCER] An Area
Stress warning has been issued.

337
00:18:57,083 --> 00:18:58,666
[MIKA] I said
this would happen!

338
00:18:58,750 --> 00:19:01,958
There's no way we can handle
a stress warning this big!

339
00:19:02,041 --> 00:19:04,666
[SAIGA] Whining is for
babies, not Inspectors.

340
00:19:04,750 --> 00:19:07,958
Inspector Shimotsuki,
we have to move out.

341
00:19:08,041 --> 00:19:09,916
But we...

342
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:13,250
Kamui's pulled off a case of
Group Psycho-Pass pollution.

343
00:19:13,333 --> 00:19:15,625
[SAIGA] I think he's
methodically probing the entire

344
00:19:15,708 --> 00:19:17,416
Sibyl System for weak points

345
00:19:17,500 --> 00:19:20,125
and exploiting
every one he finds.

346
00:19:20,208 --> 00:19:26,000
♪

347
00:19:26,083 --> 00:19:27,083
[AKANE] Kamui!

348
00:19:27,166 --> 00:19:28,625
[SHISUI gasps]

349
00:19:28,708 --> 00:19:32,458
[AKANE panting]

350
00:19:39,666 --> 00:19:42,666
[AKANE] The Dominator
doesn't even recognize him.

351
00:19:43,666 --> 00:19:45,416
[AKANE] Like he's a ghost.

352
00:19:46,208 --> 00:19:48,375
[DOMINATOR] Crime
Coefficient: Twenty-eight.

353
00:19:48,458 --> 00:19:50,791
No enforcement action required.

354
00:19:50,875 --> 00:19:53,416
Trigger will remain locked.

355
00:19:53,500 --> 00:19:54,875
[KAMUI]
So that's your color.

356
00:19:54,958 --> 00:19:57,708
It's clear, just as
I expected it to be.

357
00:19:59,916 --> 00:20:03,666
[AKANE] Who are you,
Kamui? What do you want?

358
00:20:04,750 --> 00:20:07,291
[KAMUI] Inspector Tsunemori,
when the judgment comes,

359
00:20:07,375 --> 00:20:10,041
I want you to see
it with your own eyes.

360
00:20:10,125 --> 00:20:11,750
[AKANE]
Judgment?

361
00:20:14,416 --> 00:20:16,708
[AKANE]
Hold it!

362
00:20:16,791 --> 00:20:19,208
I know you won't
fire that gun at me.

363
00:20:19,291 --> 00:20:27,041
♪

364
00:20:27,125 --> 00:20:28,541
[AKANE]
No! Stop!

365
00:20:30,583 --> 00:20:32,375
[AKANE]
What are you doing?

366
00:20:32,458 --> 00:20:35,250
I'm one of your hounds.
Let me do your dirty work.

367
00:20:35,333 --> 00:20:36,666
[gasps]

368
00:20:36,750 --> 00:20:41,375
♪

369
00:20:41,458 --> 00:20:42,875
[AKANE] No!

370
00:20:42,958 --> 00:20:52,916
♪

